"     Mario E Lacouture, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?9/6/9322/contributors\">",
"     Yevgeniy Balagula, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
